{"tid":1572660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝今日幫我阿妹返屋企嘅手足","createTime":"2019-09-15T17:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:57:54.000Z","uid":71908,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3bafeecb3cc5ef23d1477b117e0750f93de603","tid":1572660,"uid":71908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我阿妹仲係個中學生 今日去咗發夢<br />\n發完夢電話冇電 加上身上冇咩錢 喺銅鑼灣又搭唔到巴士返唔到屋企<br />\n點知有手足好好 俾咗個尿袋佢 仲俾錢佢搭的士<br />\n返到屋企附近仲有其他手足陪佢行返去<br />\n雖然我個時都發緊夢 但身為家姐嘅我完全唔佢都喺到<br />\n頭先問佢就話唔搵我係唔想我擔心...<br />\n我真係十分慚愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想多謝各位幫咗佢嘅手足 好想請各位食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我愛你哋！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"05e0d94ef7b58bec07a02756689572477e44ef5b","tid":1572660,"uid":136618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"發夢感受：家長們都好nice⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［想贏入嚟］輸乜撚嘢啊？而家先係轉捩點！！！等我用「假保險」同「私了」同大家剖析下現時情況、講解光復行動要做嘅事！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572562</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ad627834f03ae354a547bed7bd4fd59fdf38c74","tid":1572660,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"915 - 進步，改善，突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7746a2ea90d986e2bc8277c55811bc5666c503a4","tid":1572660,"uid":193534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:34:29.000Z","msg":"小心，手足一個不能少，好人一生平安"},